text: Manoj Katuwal (born 14 March 1985) is a Nepalese cricketer.Cricinfo profile He is a right-handed batsman and wicket-keeper.CricketArchive profile He played for the Nepal national cricket team between 2002 and 2006Teams played for by Manoj Katuwal at CricketArchive including the two first-class matches. == References == Category:Nepalese cricketers Category:Living people Category:1985 births
